{
  "stem": "22944.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also every flat had a little, confined part where they can keep the suitcases, boxes, things they don't use-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the laundry, the washing machine, or whatever they used to use were down in the basement.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In our basement, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the narrow basement, Pernik carved a hole a little bit bigger than the fireplace.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It seemed 4 foot by 6 foot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I still can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in front of it, he put some shelves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On the shelves, there would be jars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, things were becoming very bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I will explain to you soon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We would dash down into that hole and stay there for some time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, when things eased up a bit, we would go upstairs back to the apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, by this time, hardly any Jews in the town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All the Jews had been taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A loudspeaker-- and we could hear the loudspeaker in our apartment-- loudspeaker all over the place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anybody hiding a Jew, his life is in danger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Anybody who hides a Jew, a thousand Krone for a reward.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you could hear it all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The temptation was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Small town, small place-- we hear these loudspeakers all over the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to clear the town of Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were not going to be any more Jews left here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they are a menace to society, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the temptation was very great for Pernik, for Gavalovic, for anybody, because the-- our risk is that we're all terribly young.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The lady, Helena-- Helenka, who saved us, she was in her early 20s.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Maria was probably two years older.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
